---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Privacy, Refund & Terms" description="Privacy Policy, Refund Policy, and Terms of Service for Personalized You.">
  <div style="max-width:700px;margin:0 auto;padding:4rem 2rem;line-height:1.8;color:var(--text);">
    <h1 style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:3rem;text-align:center;color:var(--latte);">Policies</h1>

    <section style="margin-bottom:3rem;">
      <h2 style="color:var(--latte);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:1rem;">Privacy Policy</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;">Last updated: April 2026</p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;">Personalized You ("we", "us") collects personal information only when you voluntarily provide it to place an order. This includes your name, email address, and the personalization details needed to create your product.</p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;"><strong>Use:</strong> We use your information solely to fulfill your order. We do not sell, rent, or share your data with third parties.</p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;"><strong>Retention:</strong> Order data is retained for up to 90 days to handle revision requests, then deleted.</p>
      <p><strong>Contact:</strong> For privacy concerns, email us at 01jdof8eq9@gmail.com.</p>
    </section>

    <hr style="border-color:var(--border);margin-bottom:3rem;" />

    <section style="margin-bottom:3rem;">
      <h2 style="color:var(--latte);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:1rem;">Refund Policy</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;">All products are custom digital goods created specifically for each customer.</p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;"><strong>No refunds after delivery.</strong> Because your product is personalized and immediately accessible upon delivery, we do not offer refunds once the file has been sent.</p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;"><strong>Quality issues:</strong> If your delivered product does not match what you ordered, contact us within 7 days and we will revise it or issue a refund at our discretion.</p>
      <p><strong>One free revision</strong> is included with every order.</p>
    </section>

    <hr style="border-color:var(--border);margin-bottom:3rem;" />

    <section>
      <h2 style="color:var(--latte);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:1rem;">Terms of Service</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;">By placing an order you agree to these terms.</p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;"><strong>Digital goods:</strong> Products are delivered as digital files (PDF or MP3). No physical goods are shipped.</p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;"><strong>Personal use:</strong> Products are for personal, non-commercial use only. Redistribution or resale is prohibited.</p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;"><strong>Accuracy:</strong> We are not responsible for typographical errors in the information you submit. Please review your order details before submitting.</p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;"><strong>Content:</strong> We reserve the right to refuse orders that request inappropriate, offensive, or illegal content.</p>
      <p>These terms are governed by the laws of the United States.</p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
